OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMI6 head urges disaffected 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FRussians to spy for UK     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The head of MI6 has appealed to        
OL,6, Russians disaffected by the Ukraine war
OL,7, to defect and work with his            
OL,8, organisation.                          
OL,10,FIn a speech in Prague, Sir Richard     
OL,11,FMoore said many Russians were "silently
OL,12,Fappalled" to see their armed forces    
OL,13,F"pulverising" Ukrainian cities.        
OL,15,F"They are watching in horror as their  
OL,16,Fsoldiers ravage a kindred country."    
OL,18,FHe said the door was always open to any
OL,19,FRussians who wanted to join MI6 to work
OL,20,Ftogether to end the bloodshed.         
